    "content": "Poor humans!\n\nBut it's an interesting idea 🙂\n\nGoal\n* Consider adopting the rewording suggested by @N3l below.\n\n* Please format \"A\", \"B\", \"AB\", \"O\", \"+\" and \"-\" as {{constants}}.\n\nConstraints\n* Please format \"A+\", \"A-\", \"B+\", \"B-\", etc. as {{constants}}. Exclude the commas from the formatting.\n\nStub generator\n* Please simplify the write statement; I don't quite understand if there's a specific reason for using the \"join\" statement there.\n\nThanks.",
